ubsidiaries, operates an e-commerce platform for electronic products in India. The company offers development boards; drone parts; batteries, power supply, and accessories; 3D printers and parts; sensors modules; electronic components; motors, drivers, pumps, and actuators; electronic modules and displays; IoT and wireless modules; mechanical parts, measurement, and workbench tools; DIY and maker kits; and electric vehicle parts. It also provides robot making kits, e-bike accessories, microcontrollers, wheels, chassis, carbon fiber and DIY products, and other mechanical and electronic components. In addition, the company provides FDM and SLA 3D printing, prototyping, mechanical and electronic assembly, lithium-ion battery pack assembly, PCB manufacturing, and metal and non-metal laser cutting services, as well as same day shipping and customer services. It sells its products under the SmartElex, EasyMech, SimplyFly, and ProRange brands. The company serves manufacturers, industries, educational institutions, researchers, and developers. Macfos Limited was founded in 2012 and is based in Pune, India."}}